OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixture of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers for most. The showers will be
OL,7,Fheavy with the risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder in places. Windy, locally
OL,9,Fgusty in or near heavy showers or
OL,10,Fthunderstorms. Temperatures remaining
OL,11,Fbelow average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny daytime showers gradually
OL,14,Feasing to leave a largely dry night,
OL,15,Fwith clear spells developing for many.
OL,16,FFurther showers feeding in from the
OL,17,Fwest by dawn. A cool night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
