OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother day of sunny spells
OL,6,Fand showers. The showers will be heavy
OL,7,Fat times, with the risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. Breezy, locally gusty in or
OL,9,Fnear heavy showers. Cool.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,12,Fand freshening winds will spread
OL,13,Feastwards Thursday. Drier and brighter
OL,14,Fon Friday, but still on the breezy
OL,15,Fside. Dry with sunny spells Saturday.
OL,16,FTemperatures trending warmer by the
OL,17,Fweekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
